// Uninstall
section#uninstall
	h2: a Uninstalling the Game
	blockquote If you do not have the game installed yet, skip this step.
	ol
		li Open Steam and go to your #[strong Library]
		li Find #[strong Fallout 4] in the list
		li Right-click on it and select #[strong Manage -&gt;Uninstall]
		li Navigate to #[code Steam\steamapps\common\] and, if present, delete the #[strong Fallout 4] folder
		li Navigate to #[code Documents\My Games] and delete the #[strong Fallout 4] folder